      "text": [
        " اَلرَّجُلِ يَتَزَوَّجُ اَلْبِكْرَ مُتْعَةً قَالَ \"يُكْرَهُ لِلْعَيْبِ عَلَى أَهْلِهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4592 - Hafs bin al-Bakhtari narrated from Abu Abdillah (as) regarding a man who marries a virgin in Mutah (temporary marriage).\nThe Imam (as) said: \"It is disliked (makruh) due to the reproach it may bring upon her family.\""
        ]
      }
